      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'WHY PEOPLE DON''T SEEK HELP


    "Just pray harder."


    "He''s not
    sick, he''s lazy."


    "What will people say

    about our family?"


    "Therapy
    is for weak people."


    "It''s a spiritual attack,

    not a medical issue."


    These
    are the voices that

    silence millions across Africa.


    Real stories.
    Real silence.

    Real consequences.'
