  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'PTSD

    When the Past Won''t Stay in the Past


    Some experiences
    leave invisible scars.

    PTSD is one of them.


    WHAT IS PTSD?

    Post
    Traumatic Stress Disorder happens

    when a traumatic event continues to

    affect
    your daily life long after it ends.


    IN AFRICA

    Conflict, poverty and
    loss

    leave millions with PTSD.

    Yet it remains one of the most

    undiagnosed
    conditions on the continent.


    SIGNS TO WATCH FOR

    Flashbacks and nightmares

    Feeling
    constantly on edge

    Avoiding people and places

    Emotional numbness


    Healing
    is possible.

    Help is available.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
