  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'DEPRESSION

    More Than Just Sadness


    Depression is not a bad day.

    It
    is a medical condition that

    traps people in darkness.


    THE REALITY

    66
    million Africans live with

    depression right now.

    Most suffer in silence.


    SIGNS
    TO WATCH FOR

    Feeling empty and hopeless

    Loss of interest in life

    Extreme
    fatigue

    Withdrawing from loved ones


    IN AFRICA

    Depression is often
    called laziness.

    It is not laziness.

    It is an illness that needs treatment.


    Recovery
    is possible.

    You deserve help.'
