  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'THE COST OF SILENCE


    Every year, silence costs

    lives across
    Africa.


    Untreated mental illness

    leads to lost education,

    broken
    families, and

    suicide.


    Speaking up is not weakness.

    It is survival.


    Break
    the silence.

    Save a life.'
