  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'STIGMA


    Look closer.


    What do you see when

    someone says
    "mental illness"?


    Weakness? Shame? Something

    to hide?


    Stigma
    is the silence we

    choose over the truth.


    It is the reason millions

    suffer
    without speaking up.


    The reflection you see

    could be anyone.

    It
    could be you.'
